%^BOLD%^%^BLUE%^The world of ShadowGate is pantheistic and includes many deities who may be worshipped by mortals.  While any mortal may make offerings to any deity to appease him or her, each mortal is also encouraged to choose a patron who will help guide the mortal's life.  The deities are based on the Forgotten Realms pantheon, with modification.  These are the deities and their spheres of influence.

%^BOLD%^%^GREEN%^Deity       Spheres of Influence
               %^BOLD%^%^WHITE%^-%^GREEN%^Domains
%^BOLD%^%^WHITE%^--------------------------------------------------
%^BOLD%^%^BLUE%^Akadi       Air/Freedom
               %^BOLD%^%^WHITE%^-%^BLUE%^Air, Storms, Travel
%^BOLD%^%^RED%^Anhur       Valor/Vindication/War/Storms
               %^BOLD%^%^WHITE%^-%^RED%^Good, Storms, War
%^CYAN%^Auppenser   Psionics/Enlightenment/Serenity
               %^BOLD%^-%^RESET%^%^CYAN%^Creation, Knowledge, Mentalism
%^BOLD%^Auril       Cold/Ice/Winter
               %^BOLD%^-Air, Cold, Evil
%^BOLD%^%^BLACK%^Bane        Tyranny/Strife/Fear/Revenge/Retribution
               %^BOLD%^-%^BLACK%^Evil, Tyranny, War
%^BOLD%^%^MAGENTA%^Beshaba     Misfortune/Poison/Disease/Decay
               %^BOLD%^-%^MAGENTA%^Evil, Fate, Trickery
%^MAGENTA%^Cyric       Deception/Lies/Illusions/Undeath
               %^BOLD%^-%^RESET%^%^MAGENTA%^Evil, Illusion, Trickery
%^ORANGE%^Grumbar     Earth/Craft/Artifice
               %^BOLD%^-%^RESET%^%^ORANGE%^Cavern, Creation, Earth
%^CYAN%^Helm        Guardians/Protection
               %^BOLD%^-%^RESET%^%^CYAN%^Protection, Strength, Vigilance
%^BOLD%^%^CYAN%^Istishia    Waters/Purification/Oceans
               %^BOLD%^-%^CYAN%^Plant, Storms, Water
%^GREEN%^Kelemvor    Death/The Dead
               %^BOLD%^-%^RESET%^%^GREEN%^Fate, Protection, Repose
%^BOLD%^%^RED%^Kossuth     Fire/Corruption/Prophecy/Summer
               %^BOLD%^-%^RED%^Destruction, Fire, Renewal
%^YELLOW%^Lathander   Dawn/Sun/Renewal/Athletics/Spring
               %^BOLD%^-%^YELLOW%^Good, Sun, Renewal
%^RED%^Malar       Hunters/Bloodlust/Beasts
               %^BOLD%^-%^RESET%^%^RED%^Animal, Evil, Strength
